PROBLEM STATEMENT: Design a webpage using CSS box model, incorporating margins,
padding and borders
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
 <title>Box Model Demo</title>
 <style>
 div {
 background-color: lightgrey;
 width: 300px;
 border: 15px solid green;
 padding: 50px;
 margin: 20px;
 }
 </style>
</head>
<body>
 <h2>Demonstrating the Box Model</h2>
 <div>This text is the content of the box. We have added a 50px padding, 20px margin and
a 15px green border. </div>
</body>
</html>
